Warn on max
required_capability: approximation_v5

SET approximation=true\;
FROM many_numbers
| STATS max=MAX(sv) BY sv | SORT max | LIMIT 3
;

warning:line 3:13: approximation not supported: aggregation function [MAX(sv)] cannot be approximated

